3dengfx 0.1 - installation instructions
---------------------------------------

3 step installation....

1) edit config.h (by hand :) and comment-out the line that says
	#define SINGLE_PRECISION_MATH
   if you wish to make the library use floats everywere instead of
   doubles.
   No other configuration options available yet

2) make
3) make install

that's all, ready to use, se README for details

Requirements
------------
OpenGL
SDL
libpng
libbz2 (not needed yet under windows, not used)
Cg toolkit (from nvidia)
